high_descs: Walk to the end of the passage and turn right to enter the bedroom and walk to the bed.
Pick up the dumbbell from the bed.
Turn around and walk into the passage and turn left and reach the sidetable with the microwave.
Put the dumbbell on the sidetable in front of the microwave.
Move left to face the fridge.
Take out the dumbbell from the fridge.
Move right to reach the sidetable with the microwave.
Put the dumbbell on the sidetable in front of the other weights.
anns.task_desc: Put two dumbbells on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go towards the wall straight ahead, then enter the bedroom on the right, going towards the bed.
Pick up the dumbbell from the bed.
Turn around and exit the sidetable, take the left into the next sidetable, then go right all the way to the microwave.
Place the dumbbell on the sidetable the microwave is on.
Go to the fridge to the left of the microwave.
Remove the dumbbell from the fridge.
Go back to the sidetable with the microwave.
Place the dumbbell on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two Dumbbells on a SideTable.

high_descs: Go straight ahead into the narrow path, then right into the bedroom, approaching the bed ahead.
Pick up the dumbbell from the bed.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn left, and go right towards the microwave against the wall.
Place the dumbbell on the table the microwave is sitting on.
Go to the fridge just to the left.
Remove the dumbbell from the fridge.
Turn back to the table the microwave is on.
Put the dumbbell on the table next to the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two dumbbells on a small table.
